{"tid":1795574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘭桂坊協會指平安夜餐廳訂枱率約50% 整體生意跌2至3成","createTime":"2019-12-24T04:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T10:47:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfaa7d566e520c2996c21e2b30dc78ed1d12956","tid":1795574,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:14:28.000Z","msg":"今晚是平安夜（24日），預料大批市民會外出歡度佳節。受反修例風波影響，飲食業界均指生意下跌。蘭桂坊協會總監張素媚表示，本月初開始社會運動稍為緩和，市面大致平靜，近日酒吧亦開始多了客流及訂枱。不過她說，今晚平安夜餐廳一般只有約50%訂位。<br />\n<br />\n張素媚在一個電台節目上表示，相對晚市，今年午市的情況比往年好，指有客人希望特別日子外出用膳，但又不想夜晚外出，選擇了午市時間慶祝。她說，幸「午市」補救，整體蘭桂坊的生意較往年下跌2至3成。<br />\n<br />\n為應付人流，警方今日至明日（25日）在港島實施人流安全管理措施和特別交通安排。警方稱，有需要時會在蘭桂坊實施人潮管制，如有突發情況，會因應公共安全及公共秩序的風險，考慮是否需要封閉該區。張素媚回應指，蘭桂坊每當有大型節慶，都會實施臨時封路和人流管制措施，如果發生特別事故，有關部門會按根據守則和法例按照專業去處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191224/_2019122410493115003.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191224%2F_2019122410493115003.jpeg&h=8760b937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1666836/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E8%98%AD%E6%A1%82%E5%9D%8A%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E6%8C%87%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%89%E5%A4%9C%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E8%A8%82%E6%9E%B1%E7%8E%87%E7%B4%8450-%E6%95%B4%E9%AB%94%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E8%B7%8C2%E8%87%B33%E6%88%90</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0e98566add4582cde80ca21b567c098402ce2651","tid":1795574,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"撐popo啊嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15620f43060726ab53f2dfdfb5e7ae6944a79d8","tid":1795574,"uid":285371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:18:33.000Z","msg":"不完美，可改善"},{"pid":"356e39315245676c6da721813bcb5280e34c8af4","tid":1795574,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf03172ab947631717d7bada110138e8130790e","tid":1795574,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9674aad26bbfa6e165587ea9f6b9630d0cb3c5","tid":1795574,"uid":123408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"繼續攪炒"},{"pid":"e7080bfc25f46e08025d7d37a1670fdfc6d347a0","tid":1795574,"uid":297897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:47:58.000Z","msg":"跌咁少..."}]}